(22, 'Sanskrit Phrase Calligraphy', 12, 18, '<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Graphik Webfont&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">\"Atithi Devo Bhavah\" is a Sanskrit phrase that translates to - Our guests are revered as we would revere God. In Hindu culture a guest is treated with utmost respect and the service of a house guest is considered a noble task. This phrase is commonly believed in and practised in most Indian cultures and households. This beautifully calligraphed artwork, written in Devanagari script, will add a splash of colour and culture to a guest room, an entryway or any wall space.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Graphik Webfont&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Graphik Webfont&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Graphik Webfont&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This artworks comes in two colours and two sizes, A4 and 12x18 inches, both of which are standard and frames for these sizes should be easily available online or in local stores. The A4 sized artwork can be easily printed on a home or office printer on your standard paper. For the 12x18 inch size, a local printing shop should be able to do the job.</span>', '2021-04-14 11:18:54', '2021-04-14 11:18:54', 1, 'Sanskrit-Phrase-Calligraphy', 'f47454d1d3644127f42070181a8b9afc.jpg'),
